data.description: Beautiful home located on a corner lot close to schools, shopping & much more.  The home has a large living room with vaulted ceilings & gas fireplace on the main floor .  The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances & a large pantry as well. The large master suite on the main level with its own separate door to the rear deck! The master bathroom features a nice tile shower with glass enclosure as well as  the corner soaking tub  that is perfect to unwind after a long day! The laundry room is on the main level for added convenience. Upstairs has a  bonus/family room, 2 additional bedrooms with a bathroom. Outside, the yard is fully landscaped and has a drip system, low maintenance yard, wood deck and Plenty of parking with the  2-car garage. This home also has,  water softener, central air & fenced backyard! This home is a must see! Schedule your showings today!
